<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Section Number="0092.52" xmlns="http://StatRev.xsd"><Catchline xml:space="preserve">Affirmation equivalent to oath.</Catchline><SectionBody><Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">Whenever an oath shall be required by any law of this state in any proceeding, an affirmation may be substituted therefor.</Text></SectionBody><History xml:space="preserve">RS 1300; GS 1731; RGS 2946; CGL 4670; s. 3, ch. 76-237; s. 1, ch. 77-77; s. 22, ch. 78-361; s. 1, ch. 78-379.</History><Note><Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">Former s. 90.02.</Text></Note></Section>